values.value: YOUR PLAN COVERS THE ELIGIBLE EXPENSE AMOUNT REIMBURSABLE UNDER YOUR PLAN FOR COVERED OUT-OF-NETWORK HEALTH SERVICES. THE ELIGIBLE AMOUNT IS BASED ON A DATABASE OF COMPETITIVE FEES FOR SIMILAR SERVICES OR SUPPLIES IN YOUR AREA. BENEFITS ARE NOT AVAILABLE FOR THAT PORTION OF THE CHARGE THAT EXCEEDS THE ELIGIBLE AMOUNT DETERMINED FOR THIS SERVICE.
